    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Start之后设备应该发送客户端问候消息对吧？我记为SendClientHello，然后等待服务器响应。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Start",
        "SendClientHello",
        "WaitServerHello"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，收到有效的ServerHello后，设备要执行DeriveHPKE来派生加密密钥，这个步骤很关键。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WaitServerHello",
        "DeriveHPKE",
        "valid ServerHello"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，密钥派生完成后进入认证阶段。我添加SendAuth发送认证信息，然后进入WaitAuth等待认证结果。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeriveHPKE",
        "SendAuth",
        "WaitAuth"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "WaitAuth这里需要分支：认证成功进入Established状态，失败则进入Error状态终止流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WaitAuth",
